workouts.title: Workout
workouts.introText:
If you want a powerhouse lower body, there is no skipping leg day. This session will get those big muscle groups working at full capacity.


Nail your form with the tutorial, then carve out the reps at your pace.

groups.title: Warm-up
groups.summary: There are major muscle groups in your lower body, so get them primed to work.

groups.title: Round 1
groups.summary: Get your quads firing on all cylinders.

groups.title: Round 2
groups.summary: Nail your form to get your glutes and legs burning.

groups.title: Round 3
groups.summary: You'll be building shape and stability with every lunge.

groups.title: Round 4
groups.summary: Control the pace of lowering your calf to max the benefits.
